The tests are run with the Please build tool https://please.build/

> plz test

to run a subset of tests e.g. unit tests:

plz test //library/credit_card/contracts/tests/unit:credit_card_test

For simulator tests only

Add your service account token and core API URL (e.g.
https://core-api-staging.my-environment.tmachine.io/) to
"common/test_utils/contracts/simulation/test_config"
